Project: Finan - personal and group finance manager

Stack:
- Frontend: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, React Router, Axios
- Backend: Express, TypeScript, Drizzle ORM
- Database: PostgreSQL
- AI: Claude API (Anthropic) for saving tips and analytics
- Auth: JWT + bcrypt

Database:
- users, groups, group_members, categories
- transactions, budgets, goals, goal_contributions

Conventions:
- Always use TypeScript, no 'any'
- async/await only, no callbacks
- Validate inputs with Zod on server
- REST API prefix: /api/v1
- JWT stored in httpOnly cookie
- Handle all errors with try/catch
- Drizzle ORM for all DB queries, no raw SQL

Structure:
- server/src/routes/ - Express routers
- server/src/services/ - business logic
- server/src/db/schema.ts - Drizzle schema
- client/src/pages/ - page components
- client/src/api/ - axios requests